1st
copy the repo url
2nd
in my workspace do git init to initilize git
3rd
git clone url
4th
cd enter to the repo
5th 
do the needfull changes
6th
git add filename / git add .(changes will move to staging area) after doing git add use "git status" to check whether the file is in staging area or in locqal repo
7th
git commit -m "commit msg"   (provide commit msg to understand why i make changes)
8th
git push (It will push the changes to remote repo)

